entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have gained Jak Chucka's trust and respect.  Now you may be able to get that Gungan record bauble decrypted for Broma Lak.
entries.journal_entry_description: Broma Lak directed you to a Gungan informant named Jak Chucka.  Before Jak will decrypt the Gungan record bauble, he wants some...problems taken care of.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Jak has agreed to translate the bauble for you, but only after you complete three tasks for him.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You have completed your end of the contract. Return to Jak Chucka so he can fulfill his.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Jak is feeling hemmed in by hostile elements and wants you to map out the best escape route, should one be needed.

entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Some of the plants near Theed give tasty nectar this time of year. Jak wants at least four jugs of it.  They grow all over the shoreline south of Jak.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: The nesting kaadu atop the hill make too much noise for Jak to conduct business.  Thin the herd by at least 5.
